Info taken from https://github.com/Mythologyli/MicroPython-ESP32-S3-N16R8
Note: The ESP-IDF build system does not support spaces in the paths to either ESP-IDF or to projects.

Install ESP-IDF
===============
cd $HOME
mkdir -p ~/esp
cd ~/esp
git clone -b v4.4 --recursive https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf.git
cd ~/esp/esp-idf
./install.sh esp32,esp32s3

Install Micropython
===================
cd $HOME
git clone -b v1.19.1 https://github.com/micropython/micropython.git

Install Board config
====================
cd $HOME
git clone https://github.com/Mythologyli/MicroPython-ESP32-S3-N16R8.git
cp -r MicroPython-ESP32-S3-N16R8/GENERIC_S3_N16R8 micropython/ports/esp32/boards

Start a terminal session
========================
cd $HOME
. $HOME/esp/esp-idf/export.sh
cd micropython/ports/esp32
make submodules
export IDF_TARGET=esp32s3
make BOARD=GENERIC_S3_N16R8

Flash the chip
==============
Previous steps will build micropython.bin in ~/micropython/ports/esp32/build-GENERIC_S3_N16R8. Bootloader is under that in bootloader directory, partition table is in partition_table directory

C:\Users\mike\OneDrive\Documents\ArduinoData\packages\esp32\tools\esptool_py\4.2.1\esptool -p COM13 -b 460800 --before default_reset --after no_reset --chip esp32s3  write_flash --flash_mode dio --flash_size detect --flash_freq 80m 0x0 bootloader.bin 0x8000 partition-table.bin 0x10000 micropython.bin
or
/home/mikealex/.espressif/python_env/idf4.4_py3.8_env/bin/python ../../../esp/esp-idf/components/esptool_py/esptool/esptool.py -p (PORT) -b 460800 --before default_reset --after no_reset --chip esp32s3  write_flash --flash_mode dio --flash_size detect --flash_freq 80m 0x0 build-GENERIC_S3_N16R8/bootloader/bootloader.bin 0x8000 build-GENERIC_S3_N16R8/partition_table/partition-table.bin 0x10000 build-GENERIC_S3_N16R8/micropython.bin
or
idf.py -p COM13 flash

Notes:
======
I got errors and had to rm -r .espressif/ and then ./install.sh esp32,esp32s3 again
The ESP-IDF build system does not support spaces in the paths to either ESP-IDF or to projects.
